CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 22, 1967, pg. 16, reads: "Pennsylvania State Association of Beauticians and Beauty Shop Owners met in quarterly session at the Penn Sheraton Hotel April 2nd. Seated left to right, Fannie Cunningham, Pittsburgh president, Evelyn Meades, 1st vice president; Cleolis Richardson, State President, Ethel Barkley, recording secretary and Marie Smith, coordinator. Standing, Margaret Fletcher, treasurer; Clifford Ellis, chairman of finance; Lois Bailey, 2nd vice president -Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Ten women, seated from left: Fannie Cunningham, Evelyn Meades, Cleolis Richardson, Ethel Barkley, Marie Smith; standing includes: Margaret Fletcher, Clifford Ellis, and Lois Bailey, in Penn Sheraton Hotel for the Pennsylvania State Association of Beauticians and Beauty Shop Owners quarterly session
